title: LFM - Looking for a good Top and Mid Laner who range from high silver to low gold

replies.body: Im interested, but im not sure if im able to. I was in silver 1 and then was on a losing streak and now im in silver 3. I main mid Azir & LeBlanc, but can still play any midlane champion.
Im interested, currently gold 3, add me on my smurf (Galaxy Centre) since im trying to level it up whilst looking for a ranked team
